data.title: Robert Eugene “Bob” Singley (1930
data.meta_description: Published January 7, 2015 - Press Enterprise  Robert E. “Bob” Singley, age 84, 15 Klingerville Lane, Bloomsburg, died at 3:05 PM Monday, January 5, 2015 in Geisinger-Bloomsburg Hospital, where he had been a patient for one week.
